01:40:52,342 --> 01:40:53,782
the scolding was over.

2043
01:40:53,782 --> 01:40:58,678
“If I was one of your little scholars
hyeh in Bear Creek schoolhouse,

2044
01:40:58,678 --> 01:41:01,623
yu’ could learn me to like
such frillery I reckon.

2045
01:41:01,623 --> -1:59:59,000
But I’m a mighty ignorant, growed-up man.

2046
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
”

2047
01:41:04,881 --> -1:59:59,000
“So much the worse for you

2048
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
!”

2049
01:41:06,444 --> 01:41:08,796
said Molly.

2050
01:41:08,796 --> 01:41:10,320
“No.

2051
01:41:10,320 --> 01:41:12,360
I am pretty glad I am a man.

2052
01:41:12,360 --> -1:59:59,000
Else I could not have learned the thing
you have taught me.

2053
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
”

2054
01:41:16,645 --> 01:41:19,255
But she shut her lips and looked away.

2055
01:41:19,255 --> 01:41:24,202
On the desk was a letter
written from Vermont.

2056
01:41:24,202 --> 01:41:29,222
“If you don’t tell me at once when you
