01:41:29,222 --> 01:41:31,356
“never hope to speak to me again.

2058
01:41:31,356 --> 01:41:34,738
Mary Wood, seriously, I am suspicious.

2059
01:41:34,738 --> 01:41:37,048
Why do you never mention him nowadays?

2060
01:41:37,048 --> 01:41:41,045
How exciting to have you bring a
