2064
01:41:49,511 --> 01:41:51,026
So the letter ran on.

2065
01:41:51,026 --> 01:41:55,132
It recounted the latest
home gossip and jokes.

2066
01:41:55,132 --> 01:41:59,546
In answering it Molly Wood had taken no
notice of its childish

