2071
01:42:13,151 --> -1:59:59,000
till I need him.

2072
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
”

2073
01:42:14,165 --> 01:42:15,764
“Thank you so much!

2074
01:42:15,764 --> 01:42:16,684
but I wish⁠—”

2075
01:42:16,684 --> 01:42:19,853
“I reckon yu’ can’t stop me
lendin’ Taylor a hawss.

2076
01:42:19,853 --> 01:42:23,167
And you cert’nly’ll get sick
schoolteachin’ if yu’

2077
01:42:23,167 --> 01:42:25,324
don’t keep outdoors some.

2078
01:42:25,324 --> -1:59:59,000
Goodbye⁠—till that next time

2079
-1:59:59,000 --> -1:59:59,000
.

2080
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
”

2081
01:42:29,724 --> 01:42:34,538
“Yes; there’s always a next time,”
