2082
01:42:34,538 --> 01:42:36,046
“There always will be.

2083
01:42:36,046 --> 01:42:37,171
Don’t yu’ know that?”

2084
01:42:37,171 --> 01:42:38,476
She did not reply.

2085
01:42:38,476 --> 01:42:42,981
“I have discouraged spells,”
