2220
01:49:39,013 --> 01:49:42,601
so he whinnied back and quickened his
pace, and Molly started to life.

2221
01:49:42,601 --> 01:49:45,788
What was Monte doing here?

2222
01:49:45,788 --> 01:49:51,082
She saw the black horse she knew also,
