2238
01:50:45,098 --> 01:50:47,000
slack and pitifully helpless.

2239
01:50:47,000 --> 01:50:52,853
She touched the hand beside his head,
but it seemed neither warm nor cold to

2240
01:50:52,853 --> 01:50:56,365
her; she felt for the pulse,
as nearly as she could remember the

2241
01:50:56,365 --> 01:51:00,735
doctors did, but could not tell whether
