2242
01:51:00,735 --> 01:51:07,971
twice with painful care her fingers
sought and waited for the beat,

2243
01:51:07,971 --> 01:51:11,004
and her face seemed like
one of listening.

2244
01:51:11,004 --> 01:51:14,924
She leaned down and lifted his other arm
and hand from the water,

2245
01:51:14,924 --> 01:51:19,524
and as their ice-coldness reached her
senses, clearly she saw the patch near

2246
01:51:19,524 --> 01:51:24,863
the shoulder she had moved grow wet with
