sitting straight beside him,

2249
01:51:33,776 --> 01:51:39,109
staring, and murmuring aloud,
“I must not faint; I will not faint;”

2250
01:51:39,109 --> 01:51:44,176
and the standing horses looked at
her, pricking their ears.

2251
01:51:44,176 --> 01:51:49,284
In this cup-like spread of the ravine the
sun shone warmly down,

2252
01:51:49,284 --> 01:51:53,675
the tall red cliff was warm,
