2253
01:51:53,675 --> 01:51:58,123
green; outside the shade across Bear
Creek rose the steep,

2254
01:51:58,123 --> 01:52:04,526
soft, open yellow hill,
warm and high to the blue,

2255
01:52:04,526 --> 01:52:08,796
and Bear Creek tumbled
