2256
01:52:08,796 --> 01:52:13,574
The two horses on the margin trail still
looked at the spring and trees,

2257
01:52:13,574 --> 01:52:20,479
where sat the neat flaxen girl so rigid
by the slack prone body in its flannel

2258
01:52:20,479 --> 01:52:22,863
shirt and leathern chaps.

2259
01:52:22,863 --> 01:52:24,915
Suddenly her face livened.

2260
01:52:24,915 --> 01:52:26,434
“But the blood ran!”

2261
01:52:26,434 --> 01:52:31,530
she exclaimed, as if to the horses,
